<% layout('layouts/boilerplate')%>
<style>
  @keyframes rotate {
    from {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    to {
      transform: rotate(10deg);
    }
  }

  .rotate-animation {
    animation: rotate 1s infinite alternate; /* Rotates back and forth */
  }
</style>
<div>
  <h1 class="text-center" style="color: darkgreen; font-size: 4rem">Eco Drop</h1>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 text-center py-3 rotate-animation">
      <img src="/images/icons/battery.jpg" alt="battery" class="mx-auto d-block img-fluid" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br><br>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <h4>Welcome to Eco Drop. Here you can give a second life to electronic devices by offering to other people.
      Also you can find a used device that can be useful for you instead of throwing it away or before recycling it.
    </h4>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
    <div class="feature col text-center">
      <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-success bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
        <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i>
      </div>
      <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Total E-Waste Generation</h3>
      <p>On a per capita basis, the average e-waste generated by a person in Europe was around 16.2 kg in 2019.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature col text-center">
      <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-success bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
        <i class="bi bi-lightning-fill"></i>
      </div>
      <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Importance of Responsible Recycling</h3>
      <p>Recycling electronics requires less energy than extracting and processing raw materials. This contributes to energy efficiency and helps lower the carbon footprint associated with resource extraction and manufacturing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature col text-center">
      <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-success bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
        <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
      </div>
      <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Circular Economy Potential</h3>
      <p>Transitioning to a circular economy for electronics, which emphasizes reuse, repair, and recycling, could result in a net benefit of $700 billion annually by 2030.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
